name: Umbrella Up
summary:
☂️ What Can You Do with an Umbrella?

🪂 Glide: Catch the wind and soar through the skies with your umbrella wide open!

🧗 Climb: Hook onto ledges and ropes with the umbrella handle and scale dizzying heights.

🩰 Tiptoe on the Edge: Walk on the tip of your umbrella for thrilling balance challenges!

🧲 Hook & Interact: Use your umbrella to grab objects, and complete quirky tasks.
